Here's the problem with your basic viewpoint.  Your logic chain goes like this:<br>
<br>
Wizards are fine.<br>
Wizards are balanced.<br>
Therefore, making changes would unbalance Wizards and thus be bad.<br>
<br>
The problem is your basic presuppositions are not true.  Wizards are NOT fine and NOT balanced.  The basis for your presupposition you stated above:<br>
<br>
Wizards are a raid class and are good then<br>
<br>
Which is true and not true, depending on the level and places you go.  But that's no basis for balance in any demented sense of the concept, and even Verant thankfully understands that.<br>
<br>
Further, the assumption that Wizards are balanced does NOT mean making changes that have been suggested would be bad.  Because almost all the changes suggested are BEFORE the raid level of Wizards, when even by your definition the class is not doing well. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.kestrelarts.com/images/grimicon.jpg BORDER=0> at: 8/12/01 7:58:05 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessage?topicID=524.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessage?topicID=523.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=526.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.threadControl?topicID=526.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=526.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=526.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jum